hopobject.body: How many days will it take for the cheque to clear? thanda passion booster side effects More recently, the Help to Buy scheme has given the new-build sector a significant boost, which is unambiguously good. The scheme has seen 12,500 reservations since its start in April. When it is launched in January, the second half of Help to Buy, which applies to all houses, and involves a mortgage guarantee from the Government, has the potential to provide a stimulus 10 times the size of the first part. Its extensive media coverage, alongside warnings that it will usher in a new house price boom, have persuaded some potential buyers to bring forward planned purchases.
